  Total run: 495s for 5 simulated days (~99s/day)
  ATM: 288s (58%), OCN: 137s (28%), ICE: 36s (7%), LND: 23s (5%)

FME overhead: +1.6% wallclock (+7.56s on 485s baseline).
Remapped output is small: e.g., derived fields 775K vs 107M native (720x smaller).

